webpackJsonp([0x709681936991],{4953:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Spiegel Online Relaunch",date:"06 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-06-spiegel-online-relaunch/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p>Thanks to <a href="http://www.hebig.com/archives/003986.shtml">Heiko for pointing out</a> that <a href="http://www.spiegel.de/netzwelt/netzkultur/0,1518,435448,00.html">Spiegel Online has relaunched</a> (yet again). My first impression is... I like it. They\'ve made a subtle change in the typography that makes it easier to read. For better or for worse, the <a href="http://www.spiegel.de/dienste/0,1518,419923,00.html">SpOn sidebar in Firefox</a> is the first place I look for German news. Maybe Heiko can tell me if <a href="http://focus.msn.de/">Focus</a> has a sidebar as well. Or <a href="http://www.zeit.de/">Die Zeit</a>, <a href="http://couchblog.de/webpropaganda/">Nico</a>?</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Poor Organization",date:"06 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-06-poor-organization/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"PapaScott Sells Out",date:"07 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-07-papascott-sells-out/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Poor Organization",date:"06 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-06-poor-organization/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p>How can you tell you\'ve been in Germany too long? When you think the <a href="http://www.chillmost.com/2006/09/back-from-amsterdam.html">Dutch are poorly organized</a>.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"More Einschulung",date:"03 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-03-more-einschulung/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Spiegel Online Relaunch",date:"06 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-06-spiegel-online-relaunch/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"More Einschulung",date:"03 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-03-more-einschulung/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/232972161/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="http://static.flickr.com/94/232972161_446738bae9.jpg" width="375" height="500" alt="IMG 1747" /></a></p>\n<p>As I mentioned before, starting school is a big deal here in Germany, with ceremony, presents and family gathering on par with baptism, confirmation or graduation. There was even a church service before the official ceremony at the school, so here\'s Christopher at the church with his *Schult√ºte*.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Einschulung",date:"02 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-02-einschulung/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Poor Organization",date:"06 Sep 2006",slug:"/2006-09-06-poor-organization/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:195,pageCount:1101}}}});
